query:
INSERT INTO fuel_stint_configs AS fsc (plan_id, pit_duration, fuel_tank_size, tire_change_time, add_tire_time)
                VALUES ($5, $1, $2, $3, $4)
                ON CONFLICT (plan_id) DO UPDATE 
                SET 
                    pit_duration = $1, 
                    fuel_tank_size = $2, 
                    tire_change_time = $3, 
                    add_tire_time = $4
                WHERE fsc.plan_id = $5
